<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="ear-n">ear <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪə(r)/    美 /ɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 耳；耳朵：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Walls have ears. 
隔墙有耳。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>听觉；(敏锐的) 听力：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have a keen ear 
听觉灵敏</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-all-ears">be all ears</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[非正式用语] 洗耳恭听</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="close-shut-ones-ears-to">close / shut one's ears to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>不听；不愿听</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="lend-an-ear-to">lend an ear to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>倾听</strong>  </p></div>